title: Hello!
content:
# Hello!
I'm Busyrich; A web developer, teacher, and content creator. This is my personal site. It contains information on me, my professional history, and even my blog. If you are curious what I have been up to, what makes me tick, or need to get in contact with me, you are in the right place.

## Getting Around
I have based my site design around the place I feel most comfortable, my IDE. Use the links to the far left to enjoy my content around the web. The navigation section next to them will open pages available here. The content therein will display in this pane. Other than that, just click around and try some keystrokes. There might a few secrets to find.
### Testing
This is an h3 test!
